subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
Children and Youth
lead_paragraph: Asia Muhammad, 17, lost on Monday at the U.S. Open. Yet with the tactical support of Andre Agassi and Steffi Graf, she has a chance to march in a future anniversary parade of champs.
